text:
The first day of #HongKong’s #covid19 #vaccine rollout to the public --

And #China’s #Sinovac is being offered up first.

I am outside 1 of 5 sites that is offering the jab. 70,000 people have already registered to take it. All the slots for the next two weeks are fully booked. https://t.co/kmakYCiHXW
